Title: AIR AND SOUND POLLUTION MONITORING SYSTEM 
Description : - The air & sound pollution monitoring system is a great  way  to 
improve  people’s  health  by  monitoring  dangerous  gases  in  environment. The 
system  uses  the  internet  of  things  to  measure  two  parameters- sound &air 
pollution. By  continuously monitoring  pollution level, we can protect public& 
animal health from the harmful effects of pollution.
